              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "The analytical framework for this project comes from Nicotra's \"Becoming Rhetorical\" textbook. Specifically, I'm analyzing \"Driverless Dilemma\" podcast through the lens of rhetorical appeals (ethos, pathos, logos) and the basic rhetorical situation (communicator, audience, message). Nicotra introduces these concepts in Chapter 1 (\"The Basic Rhetorical Situation\") and Chapter 3 (\"Analyzing Textual Rhetoric\"). "
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
